          TerraLib 5 - SQLite Data Access Driver
          ======================================

This folder contains an implementation of the Data Access classes
for the SQLite database engine. It can acccess spatial data
in an SQLite database. It has support for for SpatiaLite format.

Driver Dependencies:
--------------------

This driver requires the following modules in order to be built:
1. Common Runtime
2. XML
3. Plugin
4. Data Type
5. SRS
6. Geometry
7. Raster
8. Data Access

The third-party software needed:
1. SQLite
2. SpatiaLite
3. Boost.Thread
4. Boost.DateTime
5. Boost.FileSystem
6. Boost.System

More Information:
-----------------

The TerraLib 5 wiki contains a complete explanation about
the internals of this driver:
http://www.dpi.inpe.br/terralib5/wiki/doku.php?id=wiki:designimplementation:dataaccess:drivers:sqlite


